Remeber Reach 🫡

My love for airsoft is fading 🥲

Tbh 2023 was a pretty mid year when it comes to attending big airsoft events and jn many ways was a massive regression overall to my airsoft experience

Stuff like this was much more prevalent than years prior and has slowly turned something that I love doing into something that just makes me want to stop playing 

I will definitely be making some changes / different decisions of how / who I spend my time and money with when it comes to airsoft and events, I have some big things planned for 2024 that I’m excited to share and will hopefully have a much better overall experience 

At the end of the day airsoft to me is just about having fun with friends, and if it wasn’t for them I would have stopped a long time ago
